  "prompt": "Where can I see a Lamborghini in Bangalore?",
  "response": "If you're looking to see a Lamborghini in Bangalore, here are a few options:\n\n1. **Lamborghini Showroom**:\n   - **Location**: Lamborghini Bangalore is located at 20/2, Lavelle Road, Bangalore, Karnataka 560001.\n   - **Details**: You can visit the official Lamborghini showroom where you can see various models of Lamborghini cars on display. It's a great place to get a close look at these luxury vehicles.\n\n2. **Car Expos and Auto Shows**:\n   - **Events**: Occasionally, Bangalore hosts auto expos and car shows where luxury car brands like Lamborghini participate. Keep an eye on event listings in local newspapers or event websites like BookMyShow or Paytm Insider.\n\n3. **Luxury Car Dealerships**:\n   - **Location**: Some multi-brand luxury car dealerships might have a Lamborghini on display. One such place is Landmark Cars on Intermediate Ring Road, Domlur, Bangalore.\n\n4. **High-End Residential Areas**:\n   - **Areas**: You might spot Lamborghinis in affluent neighborhoods like Indiranagar, Koramangala, or Sadashivanagar, where luxury car owners often reside.\n\n5. **Social Media and Car Enthusiast Groups**:\n   - **Platforms**: Joining local car enthusiast groups on platforms like Facebook or following Instagram accounts focused on luxury cars in Bangalore might give you leads on where and when you can spot a Lamborghini.\n\nRemember to check the timings and any entry requirements before visiting the showroom or attending an event. Enjoy your Lamborghini spotting in Bangalore!",
